reviewText: This is the best game ever!
My daughter saw this advertised on one of her other DVDs. She asked for it for Christmas & plays with it almost every day. She loves that she can choose how to do her party & what happens.
At first I wasn't sure about this one.  Interactive? But let me tell you, they love it.  Sometimes I think if they use it one more time, I will go crazy, but let me tell you, it is worth it.
This was a gift for my five year old grandaughter.  It is age appropriate and everything a girl wants!  Best price onine.
I brought this DVD for my niece for New Year's this year. My niece absoultely loved this movie!!!! This movie is for any girl who have a birthday coming up and loves Bratz!!
